{"tid":722164,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Steam暑期優惠光榮三國志13威力加強版做緊310蚊","createTime":"2018-06-29T08:59:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-30T13:42:58.000Z","uid":70429,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"027cd4569ced3c28cb562f51d5938c4b04799894","tid":722164,"uid":70429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T08:59:41.000Z","msg":"光榮究竟想唔想清貨架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢連佢唯一賣得出隻驚既機會都搞到貪出面咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n與此同時,Totalwar任何一隻game都平過佢,GTA5係佢既50%,神界2平佢100蚊,DS3豪華版都係佢既50%,連較貴的文明6都大幅度平過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,佢個價可以買2次巫師<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> .<br />\n<br />\n而三國志13係一款無論戰略,三國情懷,劇情,甚至遊戲性都冇任何可觀性的四不像遊戲.<br />\n<br />\n你要戰略game,totalwar好過佢,<br />\n<br />\n你要三國情懷game,三國志11同9又好過佢,<br />\n<br />\n你要劇情game,GTA同巫師同佢根本就唔洗比,<br />\n<br />\n你要遊戲性,文明6,神界2,DS3...我講唔曬.<br />\n<br />\n而一隻冇心機整食老本甚至連對話都費事打多幾粒字既驚同公司.<br />\n<br />\n連暑期減價都減得令自己隻game少競爭力過人...<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申:持有三國志13正版,玩完後成個月覺得自己做左水魚."},{"pid":"1c49999634ac04a371b7fb271f8e21535ce03c16","tid":722164,"uid":70429,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T09:02:46.000Z","msg":"屌你老母溝女溝翻來,對話得固定2句:''夫君你回來了,今天還好嗎?'' / ''相公,和你相伴是最快樂的時光''<br />\n<br />\n連佢地自己引以為豪既特別圖畫都冇張,個樣依然係咁,少少臉紅都唔肯畫上去..<br />\n<br />\n而且溝女講緊用2000蚊買d禮物就溝到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n暑期特價310蚊就買依d咁既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50f9e29e6a2d0a13b2dc0434801c91620031f039","tid":722164,"uid":70429,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T09:05:04.000Z","msg":"如果話香港可以買光榮d牛熊證或者窩輪,<br />\n<br />\n買佢熊證同認沽發達上樓真係指日可待<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當人地totalwar已經整緊三國,比心機參考緊漢朝裝備同兵種,研究城池同文化既時候,<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你仲做緊張角個新模組<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82187de4d9ab7236ba6a96a95ec1cb9d1c4c3e4d","tid":722164,"uid":44083,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T09:05:39.000Z","msg":"玩信長好過啦"},{"pid":"c9de660bbdfc7545684bc162bff6c99ecb8c27f5","tid":722164,"uid":135060,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T09:06:44.000Z","msg":"原價果陣買左 玩左10個鐘已經後悔到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19681854199d43c755e73689d5874b6eef02b961","tid":722164,"uid":70429,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T09:08:48.000Z","msg":"跟住有人可能會問,<br />\n<br />\n點解信長個樣同曹操一樣,<br />\n<br />\n點解張露個樣同今川義元一樣,<br />\n<br />\n點解立花宗茂個樣同趙雲一樣blablabla..<br />\n<br />\n點解真田個樣同太史慈一樣blablablaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaa<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n人地根本就唔會有心唔會得閒同你畫過,<br />\n<br />\n人地打算頭髮加d色,盔甲換成日本將軍甲就當日本將軍用,<br />\n<br />\n或者日本將軍甲換成漢服漢武將甲就當三國武將用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我自己講緊咩??我唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n日本d漢服同中國d漢服其實喺光榮入面好似一樣..漢服武將/文官甚至連換都唔洗換.."},{"pid":"d92032fc4470f5d13fb1908a4f41e26e46148d96","tid":722164,"uid":70429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9de660bbdfc7545684bc162bff6c99ecb8c27f5","tid":722164,"uid":135060,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T09:06:44.000Z","msg":"原價果陣買左 玩左10個鐘已經後悔到仆街